---
title: Masala Chicken & Potato Curry with Garlic Flatbread & Yoghurt
description: Some may say that a potato curry is good in the winter, but with Mumbai spiced chicken it will be hard to resist. The curry is
popping with potato chunks soaking up the coconut sauce with help from flatbreads so not a drop is missed. It’s curry any day,
every day!
